WEBVTT

00:08:26.911 --> 00:08:31.502
But the main thing about Paul
is he was so curious about everything.

00:08:32.368 --> 00:08:34.942
CA: And that's a trait
you share as well, I've noticed.

00:08:34.966 --> 00:08:38.014
You're one of the world's
great knowledge absorbers.

00:08:38.038 --> 00:08:40.188
BG: Yeah, thank God for the internet,

00:08:40.212 --> 00:08:44.022
it helps you keep track
of all the amazing things going on.

00:08:44.046 --> 00:08:47.252
Nobody gets to be
totally polymathic nowadays,

00:08:47.276 --> 00:08:48.987
because there's so many fields,

00:08:49.011 --> 00:08:52.029
whether it's biology or quantum computing.

00:08:52.053 --> 00:08:57.935
